  "remarks": "TAi.150 Title: Haji. Senior member of the Haqqani Network (TE.H.12.12.), which operates out of North Waziristan in the Federally Administered Tribal Areas of Pakistan. Has previously traveled to, and raised funds in, Dubai, United Arab Emirates. Brother of Jalaluddin Haqqani (TI.H.40.01.) and uncle of Sirajuddin Jallaloudine Haqqani (TI.H.144.07.).  ; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 9 Feb. 2011 (amended on 1 Jun. 2012 and 22 April 2013)",
